description: Use the DescribeAccountSubscription operation to receive a description of an Amazon QuickSight account's subscription. A successful API call returns an AccountInfo object that includes an account's name, subscription status, authentication type, edition, and notification email address.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID associated with your Amazon QuickSight account.

nested_items.name: AccountInfo
nested_items.description: A structure that contains the following elements:
The edition of Amazon QuickSight that your account is using.
The notification email address that is associated with the Amazon QuickSight account.
The authentication type of the Amazon QuickSight account.
The status of the Amazon QuickSight account's subscription.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
